  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = <gallery>\nWaffles.png|Normal\nWaffles (Pig Fiesta).png|Pig Fiesta\n</gallery>\n|image = Waffles Dropped.png\n|spoil = 6 Days\n|stack = 40\n|hpRestored = 60\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime = 10 sec\n|priority = 10\n|soldBy ={{Ham}}: {{Pic|32|The Sterling Trough Deli}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;10)\n|spawnCode = \"waffles\"\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Butter}}x1 {{Pic|32px|All eggs}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Berry}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|]]\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = I'm waffling on whether I should add more syrup.\n|willow = Hi, waffles!\n|wolfgang = Why does bread have holes?\n|wendy = They're definitely waffles.\n|wx78 = ERROR: TOO DELICIOUS!\n|wickerbottom = Salutations, waffles.\n|woodie = I prefer flapjacks.\n|maxwell = An excellent start to the morning. Or evening.\n|wagstaff = Waffles made without flour. What a wonderful place this is!\n|wigfrid = Waffles are nö way tö prepare för battle!\n|webber = Yummy!\n|walani = Brunch!\n|warly = Oh, brunch, I have missed you so!\n|woodlegs = Just like me mum used ta open from th'package.\n|wilba = WAFFLES BE'ETH GOOD EATS!\n|wormwood = Yum\n|wheeler = I'm eating them for dinner because I'm adventurous.\n|winona = Bet I can fit them all in my mouth.\n|wortox = The mortals like these a lot.\n|wurt = Fluffy sweet squares!\n|walter = Breakfast!\n|wanda = They're definitely waffles.\n|choose = woodie\n}}\n'''Waffles''' is a [[Food]] [[item]] cooked in the [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Butter]], 1 [[Eggs|Egg]], and 1 [[Berries|Berry]]. It is the second best [[Health]] restoring food and provides 60 {{Hp}}, 37.5 {{Hunger}}, and 5 {{Sanity}} (the first being [[Mandrake Soup]], restoring 100{{Hp}}). It takes 10 seconds to cook. '''Waffles''' are a difficult food to obtain due to needing butter, which has a 2% chance of dropping from [[Butterfly|butterflies]]. [[Eggs]] are also another factor which limits you from getting waffles early-game.\n\nAdding a [[Mandrake]] may result in Mandrake Soup. In the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, adding [[Wobster]] or [[Shark Fin]] will instead result in [[Lobster Dinner|Wobster Dinner]] and [[Shark Fin Soup]] respectively.\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires: [[File:Butter.png|link=Butter]]\n* Requires: [[File:Berry.png|link=Berries]] [[File:All Juicy Berries.png|link=Juicy Berries]]\n* Requires: [[File:Eggs Crock Pot.png|link=Eggs]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = All eggs\n|item3 = Berry\n|item4 = Filler\n|result = Waffles\n|tool = Crock Pot\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = Egg\n|item3 = Berries\n|result = Waffles\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|item4=Twigs|note={{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for Waffles that preserves as much hunger value as possible.}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = Small Eggs\n|item3 = Berry\n|count3 = 2\n|result = Waffles\n|tool = Crock Pot\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = Tallbird Eggs\n|item3 = Berry\n|item4 = Sweetener\n|result = Waffles\n|tool = Crock Pot\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = Tallbird Eggs\n|item3 = Berry\n|item4 = Mandrake\n|result = Waffles\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|note = 50% chance to result in [[Mandrake Soup]]\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Butter\n|item2 = Eggs\n|item3 = Berry\n|item4 = Ice\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Waffles\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage ==\n{{Recipe\n|item = Waffles\n|tool = Pig Icon\n|result = Manure\n}}\n== {{Pic32|Prototype}} Tips ==\n* Waffles serve as a good alternative for Warly to make use of butter in the absence of honey and sufficient fruit for [[Fresh Fruit Crepes]]. In both Shipwrecked and Hamlet, certain trees will drop eggs, though in Shipwrecked [[Jungle Tree|Jungle Trees]] will also drop banana that can satisfy the fruit requirement for Crepes.\n\n== {{Pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n[[File:Waffles (Pig Fiesta).png|right]]\n* During the [[Pig Fiesta]] event in the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, Waffles takes on a more festive appearance.\n*Despite using [[Eggs]] as an ingredient, Waffles are technically considered to be vegan. As such, [[Wurt]] can eat it, [[Wigfrid]] cannot, and [[Bunnymen]] will not be hostile to anyone carrying one. This particularly contrasts as Eggs themselves are universally considered [[Meats]], and are not vegan.\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nCD waffles.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nWaffles 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[ru:Вафли]]\n[[fr:Gauffres]]\n[[pl:Gofry]]\n[[vi:Bánh Quế]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Fruits]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]"
